Amanda Judith Sourry Knox   President of Foods, Unilever N.V.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 3 different industries.53--
Background

		Ms. Amanda Judith Sourry Knox has been President of Foods at Unilever PLC since October 01, 2015. Ms. Sourry has been President of Foods at Unilever N.V. since October 2015. She served as Senior Vice President and General Manager of US Foods Business Team at Unilever United States, Inc. since January 2008 and this team managed all of Unilever's Foods businesses in the United States excluding the U.S. Ice Cream business. She joined Unilever 1985. She served as Executive ... Vice President of Global Hair, Executive Vice President and Chairman of Unilever UK and Ireland and Executive Vice President of Global Spreads and Dressings. Ms. Sourry served as Vice President and General Manager of Meal Solutions and New Vitality of Unilever United States, Inc.Read Full Background




